The game difficulty increases with the level.
There are several game modes:
- Classic: the game difficulty increases with the level, the games can be wrong three times
- Speed: you have less than 1 second to memorize the tiles locations
- Crazy: it will drive you crazy!
- Impossible Mission: probably one of the most difficult modes
- Endurance: quite easy but be patient
- Kamikaze: very hard, no mistake is allowed (0 lives)
Be the best on each mode & test how good your short term memory is." />

